Package: leakgorilla
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), python3-requests, python3-bs4
Maintainer: Jeffrey Hawchab <your-email@example.com>
Description: Advanced web secret scanner
 LeakGorilla is a powerful tool that crawls websites and scans for
 exposed API keys, credentials, and other sensitive information.
 .
 Features:
  - Detects 20+ types of secrets (OpenAI, Claude, AWS, etc.)
  - Crawls websites recursively
  - Scans HTML and JavaScript files
  - JSON and text output formats
Homepage: https://github.com/jeffryhawchab/leakgorilla
